name: sycamoreone.github.io
body: > Listen! Sycamore One? Sycamore Two? Horse Chestnut? Willow One? Willow Two? Oh, don't stop what you are doing, it's just ... You listening, Elm? Oh, please yourself. It's just I have an important announcement to make! I have decided ... I have made a decision. I've thought about it seriously and responsibly, and - all things considered - it's the right thing for me. I feel good about it. And here it is. I will go mad.
